{"tid":389724,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)加蠟味海盜2 3 4 5","createTime":"2017-09-06T13:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T14:32:57.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31565f67d97209ff450e1f1df1271d0fd769d9db","tid":389724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb15ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=988da098\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb15ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0eb2ed01\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有dailymotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb15ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6389f69c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/06/Pirates_of_the_Caribbean_Dead_Men_Tell_No_Tales_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F06%2FPirates_of_the_Caribbean_Dead_Men_Tell_No_Tales_Poster.jpg&h=de3b0823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.威爾&middot;特納和伊莉莎白&middot;史旺的婚禮被東印度貿易公司的庫特勒&middot;貝克特勛爵打斷，後者手持拘捕令，要以一年前幫助傑克&middot;史派羅船長逃脫絞刑的罪名逮捕兩人。貝克特還持有海軍准將詹姆斯&middot;諾林頓（James Norrington）的拘捕令，但此人已經辭職且去向不明。伊莉莎白被關進監獄，貝克特派威爾去尋找斯派羅的指南針，承諾只要找到，就會赦免他和伊莉莎白。據說這個指南針有非常神奇的功能，擁有它的人無論想前往何處，指南針都會指出正確的方向。威爾出發後不久，伊莉莎白的父親威瑟比&middot;史旺（Weatherby Swann）總督潛入監獄把女兒放了出來，準備兩人一起逃出羅亞爾港。威瑟比被貝克特的助手默瑟（Mercer）抓到，但貝克特允許伊莉莎白前去追尋自己的未婚夫.....<br />\n<br />\n2.為了霸佔海洋，獲得國王授權的庫特勒&middot;貝克特下令殺死任何幫助海盜的人，並利用大衛瓊斯來毀掉海上的任何一艘海盜船。許多人被判死刑，他們唱起了咒語迫使9大海盜首領在翻船島召開會議商量對策。可因加勒比地區的海盜統領傑克&middot;史派羅船長沒有指定繼承人，因此必須要有他的出席。哈克特&middot;巴博沙船長於是帶領威爾&middot;杜納、伊莉莎白&middot;史旺、蒂婭&middot;達爾瑪以及「黑珍珠號」海盜船的一眾船員前往營救困在大衛瓊斯魔櫃中的斯派羅........<br />\n<br />\n3.傑克&middot;史派羅船長（強尼&middot;戴普飾）到達倫敦試圖營救大副約夏米&middot;吉布斯（Joshamee Gibbs，凱文&middot;麥克納利飾）但沒有成功，他被帶到英國國王喬治二世跟前，後者要求傑克帶隊，搶在西班牙人以前找到青春之泉。傑克的死對頭哈克特&middot;巴博沙（Captain Hector Barbossa，傑佛瑞&middot;羅許飾）在失去了「黑珍珠號」和一條腿後加入了英國皇家海軍進行私掠，他將是這次尋寶遠征的指揮官<br />\n<br />\n4.故事一開頭先是已經成爲了「幽冥飛船」船長的威爾&middot;杜納和自己年輕兒子亨利&middot;特納的對話。年幼的亨利&middot;特納花費了一番功夫才找到自己的父親，希望他能夠回到他母親和他身旁，然而威爾&middot;杜納受詛咒所束搏於「幽冥飛船」不能離開，只好狠心叫兒子回去。長大後的亨利&middot;特納爲解除父親的海洋詛咒，決定尋找擁有消除一切海洋詛咒的傳說寶物海神三叉戟，而成爲了皇家海軍船隊的船員打探三叉戟的下落..<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb15ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7d5ced94\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb15ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=cb659729\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37638fb87c5b6adc1ab6d83d33183c351da08a50","tid":389724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d22f55f5468024cd1433f0c0667de6ed0f5536","tid":389724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57518738646207cc35ad5e3bb769a57b927f29d4","tid":389724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1791e0512e4d3c02c23d8beeeb085bfc246a34","tid":389724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}